      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/ecb155/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2017-03-05T16:37:28.061Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Europa, ne krize identiteti,  eshte nje emision qe TV CANVAS  e jep çdo te djele pas lajmeve te ores 20,00. U bo 3-4 te djela qe e jep. Te interesuarit mund ta nxjerrin edhe nga interneti.<br>\nMade in Europa , quhet emisioni. <a href=\"https://www.canvas.be/made-in-europe\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://www.canvas.be/made-in-europe</a></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
